    <!-- HELP -->
    <string name="help_getting_started_content">• Set the start date of your cycle.\n• Define cycle labels (e.g. A, B or Morning, Afternoon, Night).\n• Select which label applies to the start date.\n• Configure rules (skip weekends or holidays if needed).\n• Save your settings.\n• Optionally add a widget to your home screen.</string>

    <string name="help_cycle_logic_content">• The start date is the reference point of the cycle.\n• The selected label applies to that date.\n• Each valid day advances the cycle.\n• Skipped weekends or holidays do not affect the cycle.</string>

    <string name="help_assignments_content">• Assignments add extra labels (e.g. O1, vacation, sick leave).\n• Edit a day in the 7-day preview or calendar.\n• Assignments can override or complement the cycle.\n• You can toggle assignment visibility in settings.</string>

    <string name="help_preview_content">• Shows the next 7 days based on current settings.\n• Tap a day to edit its assignment.\n• Changes appear after saving.\n• Reflects both cycle rules and assignments.</string>

    <string name="help_calendar_content">• Displays a monthly overview of the cycle.\n• Each day shows a short label (A, B, O1).\n• Tap a day to see details.\n• Combines cycle and assignment data.</string>

    <string name="help_widget_content">• The widget shows your current cycle.\n• It updates automatically every day.\n• You can customize its appearance in settings.\n• Uses the same data as the app.</string>

    <string name="help_tips_content">• Use short labels for better readability.\n• Keep the cycle simple (A/B or 2–3 shifts).\n• Use assignments for exceptions.\n• If something looks wrong, check start date and rules.</string>

    <!-- WHAT'S NEW -->
    <string name="whats_new_title">What’s New</string>
    <string name="whats_new_version_format">Version %1$s</string>
    <string name="whats_new_view_full_changelog">View full changelog</string>
    <string name="whats_new_content">✨ New\n• Templates (presets) – e.g. Pošta Slovenije A/B\n• 7-day preview with editable assignments\n• Calendar with improved day labels and details\n• Support for additional countries: Italy and Hungary\n\n🎨 Improvements\n• Redesigned Settings, Help and Statistics screens\n• Start day selection with chips UI\n• Better cycle and assignment display\n• Improved Help screen with expandable sections\n• Cleaner settings layout and display options\n\n⚙️ Fixes and stability\n• Improved notification reliability on some devices\n• Fixed Save / Revert button behavior\n• General bug fixes and performance improvements</string>

